snippet.title: Big Official Update on Aquaman 2 | Amber Heard Confirmed Or Not? | Flixet
snippet.description:
In this video, we are going to share an official update of Aquaman 2. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
_____________________________________________

If there is one movie that has instilled mixed emotion among the masses around the world, it is DC's Aquaman 2. You know why confused. Starring Jason Momoa and Amber Heard, the film made headlines for a year due to controversy. Thanks, Amber Heard for that. But while the culture of cancellation still haunts the studio and the project, the team seems to be doing well. Director James Wan has now decided to unveil the new title for the sequel.
